org.openimaj.rdf.owl2java

Class Something

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.rdf.owl2java.Something
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContainerImpl, ForumImpl, ItemImpl, PostImpl, RoleImpl, SiteImpl, SpaceImpl, UserAccountImpl, UsergroupImpl

    public abstract class Something
extends Object
    Top level class that all top-level superclasses generated from an ontology will inherit from. This allows us to add functionality to all generated classes in one single place.

    This class currently provides a single access point for:

    • retrieving and setting the URI of an instance
    • adding unvalidated triples
    • adding unvalidated relations

    During serialization, an unvalidated triples list will be sent directly to the triple sink and the field avoided. Unvalidated relations will be serialized in turn and sent to triple sink.
